metadata.name: Stage 02: DW-S2-B8J6P
metadata.description: [Report] Subject is currently at Stage 02. We started the tests on the frontal part of the brain according to protocol. We had to add additional security straps during the most recent examination, after the subject easily tore through the initial ones. Eight rounds of the new serum have been injected so far and the Lab is currently comparing the results with the ones from last week.  [End Report] - [Primary Equipment] Pliers, Dental Probe, and Damaged Experiment Cart [End Primary] - [Secondary Equipment] Damaged Chain Link Specimen Cage and Biological Transmitter [End Secondary]
